<h3 id="_7-5-常见问题与解决方案" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_7-5-常见问题与解决方案"><span>7.5 常见问题与解决方案</span></a></h3>
<h4 id="_7-5-1-问题-1-pyinstaller-不是内部或外部命令" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_7-5-1-问题-1-pyinstaller-不是内部或外部命令"><span>7.5.1 问题 1：<code v-pre>pyinstaller 不是内部或外部命令</code></span></a></h4>
<p><strong>原因：</strong> Python 的 <code v-pre>Scripts</code> 目录未添加到系统环境变量 <code v-pre>Path</code> 中。<br>
<strong>解决：</strong></p>
<ol>
<li>找到 Python 的 <code v-pre>Scripts</code> 目录（如 <code v-pre>C:\Python312\Scripts</code>）。</li>
<li>进入“系统属性”→“高级”→“环境变量”。</li>
<li>在“系统变量”→“Path”中添加上述路径。</li>
<li>重启命令行窗口。</li>
</ol>
<h4 id="_7-5-2-问题-2-打包后缺少外部文件-如-config-ini" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_7-5-2-问题-2-打包后缺少外部文件-如-config-ini"><span>7.5.2 问题 2：打包后缺少外部文件（如 <code v-pre>config.ini</code>）</span></a></h4>
<p><strong>原因：</strong> 未使用 <code v-pre>--add-data</code> 参数将外部文件指定打包。<br>
<strong>解决：</strong> 重新打包，并补充 <code v-pre>--add-data</code> 参数（Windows 使用 <code v-pre>;</code> 分隔路径）：</p>
<div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="bash" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code" v-pre=""><code class="language-bash"><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A0A1A7;--shiki-light-font-style:italic;--shiki-dark:#7F848E;--shiki-dark-font-style:italic"># 示例：打包config.ini到.exe同级，data文件夹到data子目录</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">pyinstaller</span><span style="--shiki-light:#986801;--shiki-dark:#D19A66"> --onefile</span><span style="--shiki-light:#986801;--shiki-dark:#D19A66"> --name</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> DOUBAO_QA</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> ^</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">--add-data</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> "config.ini;."</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> ^</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">--add-data</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> "data;data"</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> ^</span></span>
<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">main.py</span></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h4 id="_7-5-3-问题-3-安装-pyinstaller-时提示-winerror-2-系统找不到指定文件" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_7-5-3-问题-3-安装-pyinstaller-时提示-winerror-2-系统找不到指定文件"><span>7.5.3 问题 3：安装 PyInstaller 时提示 <code v-pre>[WinError 2] 系统找不到指定文件</code></span></a></h4>
<p><strong>原因：</strong> PyInstaller 相关进程被占用或权限不足。<br>
<strong>解决：</strong></p>
<ol>
<li>打开任务管理器，结束所有 <code v-pre>python.exe</code> 和 <code v-pre>pyinstaller.exe</code> 进程。</li>
<li>以<strong>管理员模式</strong>打开 PowerShell 或命令行，执行强制重装：<div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="bash" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code" v-pre=""><code class="language-bash"><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF">pip</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> install</span><span style="--shiki-light:#986801;--shiki-dark:#D19A66"> --force-reinstall</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379"> pyinstaller==</span><span style="--shiki-light:#986801;--shiki-dark:#D19A66">6.16.0</span></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div></li>
</ol>
<h3 id="_7-6-验证打包结果" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_7-6-验证打包结果"><span>7.6 验证打包结果</span></a></h3>
<p>运行 <code v-pre>DOUBAO_QA.exe</code> 后，进行功能和环境兼容性测试：</p>
